
            Video
            Key moments from Pope's inauguration
            The inauguration Mass for Pope Francis has been held in St Peter's Square in Rome, marking the official start of his papacy.Francis earlier toured the square in an open-topped vehicle, descending to bless pilgrims behind the barriers.His homily called on global leaders and all people of the world to protect the weak and the poor.
                
                        19 Mar 2013
                    
                
        
